hed when she developed another complication days later and was rushed to another hospital where she later died. A neighbour, who claimed to have seen her before she died of the complication, said she thought her condition was improving, “She smiled at me and waved and never was there any sign like pain, she was a nice and lively fellow” Vanguard News Nigeria. A 15-year old girl, Oghenevwede Michael has reportedly committed suicide after her parents were said to have reprimanded her for staying out late. August 17, 2018 In "Crime Alert" WHY four-year-old girl, Testimony Toke Babalola, was reportedly whipped to death by her parents in Akure, Ondo State capital few weeks ago has been unravelled. September 1, 2019 In "Metro" DETECTIVES in Ondo State have arrested a farmer in Idanre Local Government Area of the state, Mr Ojo, for allegedly killing his daughter’s lover. August 12, 2013 In "News"